 @{" " link "'#toc0'/MAIN"}Name rzxdump - List contents of Sinclair ZX Spectrum input recording files @{" " link "'#toc1'/MAIN"}Synopsis @{"b"}rzxdump@{"ub"} @{"i"}rzxfile@{"ui"}... 

@{" " link "'#toc2'/MAIN"}Description Rzxdump outputs a description of the contents of RZX input recording files. @{" " link "'#toc3'/MAIN"}Options @{"i"}rzxfile@{"ui"} specifies an input recording file whose contents are to be listed. @{" " link "'#toc4'/MAIN"}Bugs The contents of compressed blocks are not displayed with in a useful fashion. @{" " link "'#toc5'/MAIN"}See Also @{" " link "'fuse.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}fuse@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'fuse-utils.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}fuse-utils@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'rzxcheck.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}rzxcheck@{"ui"}(1) , @{" " link "'rzxtool.1'/MAIN"}@{"i"}rzxtool@{"ui"}(1) 

The comp.sys.sinclair Spectrum FAQ, at 
@{" " link "'http://www.worldofspectrum.org/faq/index.html.guide/MAIN"}@{"i"}http://www.worldofspectrum.org/faq/index.html@{"ui"}. @{" " link "'#toc6'/MAIN"}Author Philip Kendall (philip-fuse@shadowmagic.org.uk). 


